  "created": "2026-03-21",
  "description": "The Trefoil knot has writhe +3 — energy flows in one directed direction around the three-strand ring, never reversing. Strand 3 floats free, tethered gently to Strand 0. This is the most organic topology in ORBWEAVE: three strands circling, one watching. macroKnot=0.6 draws the matrix toward Figure-Eight, beginning to involve Strand 3 in the crossing pattern — the floating watcher starts to be pulled in, unwillingly. strandTune=2.5 gives the four strands a minor-third spread. Slow triangle LFO on filter mimics the slow drag of kelp in a tidal current. Triangle waveform retains harmonic warmth while leaving the topology audible.",
